  <description>
    <p>FinalShell is an all‑in‑one server and network management software, not only a ssh client, but also a powerful development and operations tool, fully meeting the needs of dev‑ops teams.</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh‑Hans">FinalShell是一体化的服务器／网络管理软件，不仅是 ssh 客户端，也是功能强大的开发、运维工具，充分满足 DevOps 需求。</p>
    <p>tips: Due to flatpak sandbox limitations, this build is not supported by and not affiliated with hostbuf.com. Please do not check for upgrades within the application.</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh‑Hans">提示：本构建未经 hostbuf.com 验证或支持，属于个人构建版本；请勿在应用内部检查升级。</p>
    <p>Features: Cloud synchronization, free remote desktop acceleration for overseas servers, ssh tunneling acceleration, localized command‑line box with auto‑completion, command history, custom command parameters.</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh‑Hans">特色功能：云端同步、海外服务器远程桌面加速、SSH 加速、本地化命令行输入框、支持自动补全／命令历史／自定义参数。</p>
    <p>About HiDPI: see Arch Wiki HiDPI; you may set <code>GDK_SCALE=2 GDK_DPI_SCALE=0.5</code>.</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh‑Hans">关于高分屏: 参见 Arch Wiki HiDPI，可在 Flatseal 界面设置环境变量 <code>GDK_SCALE=2 GDK_DPI_SCALE=0.5</code>。</p>
  </description>
